85
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,130
Thanks, Mom.

86
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:27,890
Don't worry, Mrs. Wei.

87
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,850
Even if Zhi doesn't know where to take them,

88
