- Thanks, Yiming, for helping Zhi out. - Thanks.

95
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,980
It's nothing.

96
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,610
Yeah, Mrs. Wei,

97
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,450
Zhi is capable and independent.

98
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,100
