136
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:43,930
Dig in.

137
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,930
Thanks, Mrs. Wei.

138
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,020
And about the prostheses,

139
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,290
thank you,

140
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,930
Yiming and Zhi.

141
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,700
Don't mention it.

142
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,100
