143
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:53,780
Don't worry.

144
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,290
Exactly.

145
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,730
Yiming's hospital

146
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,050
