224
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,700
Am I right?

225
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,660
In this regard,

226
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,610
Yiming is outstanding.

227
00:07:58,870 --> 00:07:59,540
Mrs. Wei,

228
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:01,700
