245
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,420
Right, Yiming?

246
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:39,490
Well,

247
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,580
not necessarily.

248
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,300
Times

249
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,820
